| Breakpoint | Ancho | Uso |
|---|----|-----|
| Default | < 640px | Mobile |
| `sm` | ≥ 640px | Mobile landscape |
| `md` | ≥ 768px | Tablet |
| `lg` | ≥ 1024px | Desktop |
| `xl` | ≥ 1280px | Desktop grande |
| `2xl` | ≥ 1536px | Ultrawide |
